<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><CollegeDeptHome ID="x40676" Name="Online Teaching Endorsement" Layout="college-dept_home.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Online Teaching Endorsement</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Online Teaching Endorsement</Abstract><xPower Type="List" Name="MainImages" label="Top Image(s) (950px width, 335px height required)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><MainImage type="imagefile" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Width="950" Border="" Alignment="" Expanded="true" Height="335" AlternateText="" HSpace="" VSpace="">Admin_Offices/continuing education/950x335/100507KendallBaron_4_1.jpg</MainImage></xPower><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="Main" label="Main Content" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true" GroupStart=""><xPower Type="LinkSet" Name="CourseHighlights" label="Course Highlights" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" QuerySchemas="" QueryLocationRoots="" Title="" Values="" LinkSet="" /><xPower Type="LinkSet" Name="FeaturedStudent" label="Featured Student" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" QuerySchemas="" QueryLocationRoots="" Title="" Values="" LinkSet="" /><FullText type="boolean" label="Check for text body to use the full width of the page." readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</FullText><TopText type="boolean" label="Check to put text body above Highlighted News" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</TopText><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Optional Content" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Height=""><![CDATA[<p>This endorsement program is targeted for currently licensed teachers and future teachers who would like to be qualified to teach online courses for public, charter, and private schools in Idaho and beyond.  The advancements of information technology have radically shifted the landscape of education.  Students are now required, as part of state graduation requirements, to take online classes in preparation for their future learning in college and their eventual careers.</p>
<p>BYU-Idaho is now preparing students for this new field of online learning by offering the online teaching endorsement.  <a href="http://www.sde.idaho.gov/site/teacher_certification/subject_area.htm#ONLINE%20TEACHER%20ENDORSEMENT%20(PRE-K-12)">Endorsements</a> (See the table of contents on this page) are given by the State Office of Education qualifying a teacher to teach in a new area or new setting.   To satisfy the state endorsement requirements, students are enrolled in an efficient and flexible competency-based program that consists of two courses.  The first course, <a href="x42012.xml">ED 210</a> (3 credits), serves as the introduction to the endorsement program.  The second course,  <a href="x40699.xml">ED 420R</a>, is a variable (1-3)credit course that is retaken until all the competencies for the endorsement are satisfied.  The rate of completion of the endorsement depends on the technological aptitude of the student and the amount of time and energy devoted to the competencies by the student.  It is estimated that the average student would need to be prepared to spend 12-15 credits to fulfill all competency requirements.</p>]]></BodyCopy></xPower><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="FaceBook" label="Facebook Integration" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" GroupStart=""><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" /><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BannerAd type="multiselect" label="Rotating Ads" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" MaxChoices="" PageSize="10" Query_PageType="BannerAdComponent" Query_LocationRoot="x32" Query_SelectedFields="@Name|@ID" AdditionalFilter_XPathQuery="" /><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="QuickLinksGroup" label="Quick Links Group" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" GroupStart=""><xPower Typ